data.title: Zuzanna Horna
data.text:
Zuzanna Horna has been playing the violin since she was 7. She is a prizewinner at numerous violin competitions e.g.

1st prize at the 17th Sopocki Violin Competition

2nd prize at the 2nd Jadwiga Kaliszewska All-Polish Violin Competition in Poznan

2nd prize at 2nd All-Polish Violin Competition “Be Like Wieniawski” in Lublin.

In 2017 she was invited to join Luslawice Talents Orchestra managed by Krzysztof Penderecki European Centre of Music. She performed with the Zielona Gora Philharmonic Orchestra during the “Polish Masters of Violin” String Festival in 2017 and 2020.
